com.nokia.maps.common

Class GeoCoordinate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nokia.maps.common.GeoCoordinate

  • public final class GeoCoordinate
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a geographical position. It consists of latitude, longitude and an optional altitude.
